# Styling Conventions

## Theme
- Dark theme with AoE2-inspired palette: golds (`amber-500`), deep blues/grays (`slate-800/900`), warm accents
- Use Tailwind utility classes — avoid inline styles
- Glassmorphism effects for panels: `bg-slate-800/60 backdrop-blur-sm border border-amber-900/20 rounded-xl`

## Typography
- Headings: `font-bold text-amber-100`
- Body text: `text-slate-300`
- Muted/secondary: `text-slate-400`
- Links/interactive: `text-amber-400 hover:text-amber-300`

## Components
- Buttons: `bg-amber-600 hover:bg-amber-500 text-white rounded-lg px-4 py-2 transition-colors`
- Cards: `bg-slate-800/80 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-4`
- Inputs: `bg-slate-900 border border-slate-700 rounded-lg`

## Animations
- Tool activity: AoE-themed pulse animations (defined in `globals.css`)
- Transitions: Use `transition-colors` or `transition-all duration-200`
- Avoid excessive motion — keep it professional
